{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Consider the following two simple HTML forms:</p>\n<form>\n<p><label>Name: </label> <input type=\"text\" name=\"name_a\" /></p>\n<p><label>Email: </label> <input type=\"email\" name=\"email_a\" /></p>\n<p>Email frequency:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><input type=\"radio\" name=\"freq_a\" value=\"daily\" /> <label>Daily</label></li>\n  <li><input type=\"radio\" name=\"freq_a\" value=\"weekly\" /> <label>Once a week</label></li>\n  <li><input type=\"radio\" name=\"freq_a\" value=\"monthly\" /> <label> Once a day</label></li>\n</ul>\n</form>\n<hr />\n<form>\n<p><label>Name: <input type=\"text\" name=\"name_b\" /></label></p>\n<p><label>Email: <input type=\"email\" name=\"email_b\" /></label></p>\n<p>Email frequency:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"freq_b\" value=\"daily\" /> Daily</label></li>\n  <li><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"freq_b\" value=\"weekly\" /> Once a week</label></li>\n  <li><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"freq_b\" value=\"monthly\" /> Once a day</label></li>\n</ul>\n</form>\n<p>Notice a difference? Here's a hintâ€”try playing around email frequency options. Notice how with the top one you have to click on the actual radio button itself, but on the bottom example you can click the label. The bottom one is easier to work with, isn't it?</p>\n<p>If you don't already know this trick, here's the HTML. For the first, less-conveneient version:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Form label<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>For the version with improved usability, there's actually two ways to accomplish this:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!--variation one--></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Form label wrapping input <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!--variation two--></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>input_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Form label<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>input_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 05, 2019","path":"/posts/form-labels","title":"Usability Hacks: Remember Your Form Labels"}}},"pageContext":{}}